Staff Picks

Helloooo Wolf IQ! By now, we've all received a gazillion Black Friday/Cyber Monday (BFCM) emails. Sure, it's a vital time of the year for store owners like you, but let's zoom out a bit.

Consider this the beginning of big things, a kickstart for your long-term success. Your approach (and the solutions you choose) right now can help you make the most of your business during this busy period - and beyond. That's why I'm here, with suggestions for tools that can help you do just that.

Erika
Woo

Klaviyo

Want to make every day count this BFCM? Look no further: Klaviyo has the marketing automation tools you need to connect with (and convert) more customers.

Send targeted emails and texts to grow your audience, boost sales, and collect product reviews you can show off. Plus, with Klaviyo's AI, you can work faster and smarter. Efficiency for the win!
Get real results with Klaviyo

WooCommerce Accommodations Bookings

Rent out your property over the holidays without handing over a chunk of your profits to a fee-hungry booking service.

This free add-on for WooCommerce Bookings works like a charm, allowing you to set rates, and specify check-in and checkout times without needing to log into a third-party platform. You've got full control!
Say goodbye to extra fees

Everglow
If you sell skincare and beauty products, you'll know just how important first impressions are. For that flawless look, you need Everglow.
This theme gives your online store the makeover it deserves, with pre-built page templates and elegant block patterns. Ready to display your brand beautifully across all devices?
Ready, set, glow

Astra Pro
Get a lightweight, ready-to-go theme

Jetpack

Save & Share Cart
Fewer abandoned carts, please
